    "en": {
      "title": "Ilayaraja became a member of Rajya Sabha of India",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The President of India can appoint 12 MPs to the Rajya Sabha who excel in various fields including sports, social service, art and literature.",
        "Accordingly, along with music composer Ilayaraja, India's former athlete PT Usha, who excelled in the field of sports, and film scriptwriter Vijayendra Prasad from Andhra have been selected and appointed as MPs.",
        "Indian Prime Minister Narendra Modi has congratulated Ilayaraja, PT Usha, who has been elected as a member of the Rajya Sabha. (a)"
      ],
